{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<msub>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>MathML<code><strong>&lt;msub&gt;</strong></code>元素用来为表达式加下标，语法如下：<code><strong>&lt;msub&gt; base subscript &lt;/msub&gt;</strong></code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"class_id_style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd>供<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">样式表</a>使用。</dd>\n <dt id=\"href\">href</dt>\n <dd>用来设置标签点击后跳转的链接。</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>用来设置标签的背景色，可以使用<code><strong>#rgb</strong></code>、<strong><code>#rrggbb</code></strong>或者<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\">HTML 颜色名</a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathcolor\">mathcolor</dt>\n <dd>用来设置标签文字的颜色，同样可以使用<code><strong>#rgb</strong></code>、<strong><code>#rrggbb</code></strong>或者<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\">HTML 颜色名</a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"subscriptshift\">subscriptshift</dt>\n <dd>用来设置下标相对于表达式的基线的最小距离，它是一个<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\">长度值</a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下述代码表示：<img alt=\"x1\" src=\"/files/3202/msub.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>您的浏览器的渲染结果：&nbsp;<math> <msub> <mi>X</mi> <mn>1</mn> </msub> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>X<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.msub\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">msub</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.msub\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">msub</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.msub","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"关于gecko的特殊说明","title":"关于 Gecko 的特殊说明","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>从 Gecko 26.0 (Firefox 26 / Thunderbird 26 / SeaMonkey 2.23 / Firefox OS 1.2)开始，不允许使用&lt;none /&gt;作为子元素。The rendering has been made more consistent with equivalent configurations of <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"<msup>\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></code> and <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt; (en-US)</a></code> and a bug with an incorrect application <code>of the </code><code>superscriptshift</code> attribute has been fixed (see <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=827713\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;827713</a> for details).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"<msup>\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></code> (Superscript)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"<msubsup>\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></code> (Subscript-superscript pair)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt; (en-US)</a></code> (Prescripts and tensor indices)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"关于 Gecko 的特殊说明","id":"关于gecko的特殊说明"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"MathML<msub>元素用来为表达式加下标，语法如下：<msub> base subscript </msub>。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<msub>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<msub>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<msub>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<msub>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/element/msub","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/element/msub/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub","title":"<msub>"}],"pageTitle":"<msub> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}